<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>Personal Combined Feed</title><link>https://example.invalid</link><description>Personal aggregate feed</description><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 13:17:45 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>Show HN: Scan domain for llms.txt LLMs-full.txt AI aware SEO tool</title><link>https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47823995</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Hi! Been working on DialtoneApp, a free domain scanning tool to see how your site does with all the new rules for AI SEO. Also known as AEO (Answer Engine Optimization) or GEO (Generative Engine Optimization) the A can also stand for "Agent"! It's a whole new world out there and we haven't even gotten to agents.json files and the new "b2b" (bot to bot) commerce part.&lt;p&gt;But there are some standards starting to take shape with llms.txt and using things like:&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://dialtoneapp.com/top-sites.md" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://dialtoneapp.com/top-sites.md&lt;/a&gt;"&gt;&lt;p&gt;on all your html pages to have this other markdown version. We list the top 300 sites in terms of how well they follow all the new rules. You are welcome to scan your domain and see how you score.&lt;p&gt;Still playing with the pricing but starting with a $9.00/month USD membership which will give a much deeper scan and continuous monitoring + support.&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://dialtoneapp.com/" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://dialtoneapp.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;Happy AI SEOing.&lt;/p&gt;
